{"tid":566811,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"辦公室派利是都參透到好多野","createTime":"2018-02-20T09:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T10:48:12.000Z","uid":172607,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4c82506388fa84d56f672bd3856ed4cf15e89531","tid":566811,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T09:05:34.000Z","msg":"未婚打工仔最期待當然係一年一度拎利是環節，除左老細封開工利是外，同事之間派唔派利是都係一門學問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1.唔少同事都會自動波見到就俾利是，咁當然會講返恭賀說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  （因為派利是唔係必然，特別係唔太熟果d）<br />\n<br />\n2.有d平時同你有講有笑，公事上都有接觸嘅，真係可以唔派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  講真 其實無人貪你10蚊20蚊，但唔識做人係死罪，意頭野都係想大家開心下<br />\n<br />\n3.有d屋企有唔開心事發生左，好識做會派朱古力俾大家，起碼俾人知道唔係特登唔派<br />\n<br />\n都係果句啦， 新年派利是開心野黎， 但都唔好特登去R利是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65103f3e6960d270bd93af898897877dcd0d92fe","tid":566811,"uid":32577,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T09:28:16.000Z","msg":"根本就唔想拎，逼住要講啲恭賀說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我而家就咁講多謝就算"},{"pid":"df0dd5e9289d4e3952f39c7c2b00d157bb4ecbed","tid":566811,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65103f3e6960d270bd93af898897877dcd0d92fe","tid":566811,"uid":32577,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T09:28:16.000Z","msg":"根本就唔想拎，逼住要講啲恭賀說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我而家就咁講多謝就算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T09:30:49.000Z","msg":"人地行到埋黎 我都會講句身體健康嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a62cc382ba5b99c0fed676eb08ed0025a13545","tid":566811,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T09:31:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"413660cb5dbb95c27c855922054d8272d981fea3","ti